0.1.name: wordpress/scgeshi
0.1.description:
Simple code highlighting plugin for your remote source files

It is powered by the GeSHi engine which supports a large number of programming languages

The plugin is using styles like Code Snippet. Thanks to Roman Roan and Wyatt Neal. In addition, I would like to thank Jürgen Mayer for making the banner of this plugin.
